#home.nav-anchor
  = image_tag 'desk-scene-titles2.png', class: 'img-fluid'


#about.nav-anchor.pad-section
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-offset-2.col-xs-8.text-xs-center
        %p
          A community-driven developer network and platform for VR/AR professionals to profile, showcase, team up and explore skilled talent and resources.
        %p
          = link_to "Join", new_profiles_path, class: 'btn btn-info btn-lg'
        %p
          Connect with people.
          %br 
          Share resources. 
          %br 
          Showcase your work. 
          %br 
          Explore in VR. 
 

#services.nav-anchor.pad-section
  .container
    %h2.text-xs-center Stake your place among the Meta.versatile
    %br
    .row.text-xs-center
      .col-sm-3.col-xs-6
        %i.fa.fa-user
        %h4 Profile
        %p Register your talents, skills and interests as a player in the virtual, augmented and mixed reality developer community. 

        
      .col-sm-3.col-xs-6
        %i.fa.fa-diamond
        %h4 Showcase
        %p Post your 3D work, browsable in VR. Including 360-degree media. 3D model gallery. VR "trailers". YouTube demo theatre.
        %p  
      .col-sm-3.col-xs-6
        %i.fa.fa-thumbs-o-up

        %h4 Reputation
        %p Self-rated skills and experience levels. Peer endorcements. Tie into your favorite social sites.
      .col-sm-3.col-xs-6
        %i.fa.fa-globe
        %h4 Community 
        %p It's about you and us. Peer audience, professional connections, sharing. 

#information.nav-anchor.pad-section
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-6
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            %h2 Project Status
          .panel.panel-default
            This project is just getting started. We're raising interest and collecting feedback at this early stage to prioritize features and usage scenarios. Getting new users on-board quickly is key. So if it looks interesting for you, please provide your email and answer a few sign-up questions. 
            %p.text-xs-center{ style: 'margin-top: 1em'}
              = link_to "Yes, I'm Interested", new_profiles_path, class: 'btn btn-info btn-lg'

            
      .col-sm-6
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            %h2 Architecture Vision
          .panel.panel-default{style:"font-size:smaller"}
            %ul
              %li Web-based interface to sign-up, build your personal profile and personal preferences. 
              %li 3D VR front-end to browse and interact.
              %li Open API for accessing data, with authentication and security. 
              %li Tools to build custom rooms to showcase your work and present your personal profile
              %li Cross-device: mobile VR (Cardboard, GearVR), desktop VR (Rift, Vive), AR (Hololens, Meta2)
              %li Support WebVR, AltspaceVR, HighFidelity and other platforms
            %p



